projects.title: Reconstruction of the administration building in Vilnius
projects.description: Reconstruction work of an administration building located at T. Ševčenkos Street 13, Vilnius, was performed. Main work: dismantling of floors, reinforced concrete structures, masonry walls, and openings. Demolition work of one part of the building, removal of construction scrap, and preparation of the territory for construction work.

projects.title: Artery business centre construction reaches an important milestone: the installation of a unique facade in the Baltic States has started
projects.description: The Artery business centre, designed by world-renowned architect Daniel Libeskind (New York, USA), is beginning to take shape in the central business district of Vilnius – Konstitucijos Avenue. Most of the monolithic reinforced concrete structures have already been erected since the start of the project, and now, beautification works have begun on the 20-storey complex with facades that require exceptional technological solutions. This is another important milestone in the development of this business centre, which is attracting the attention not only of a growing number of ordinary Vilnius residents but also of leading Lithuanian and international companies.
